text: Donald Clarke (born 15 May 1926) is an English cricketer. He played two first- class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club in 1946. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1926 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:People from Bromborough
